				<description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to configure a wireless adapter to connect to nearby access point by shell commands&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;runbook&#34;&gt;Runbook&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo systemctl start iwd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo iwctl --passphrase &amp;lt;secret&amp;gt; station wlan0 connect &amp;lt;accesspoint&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo systemctl start dhcpcd@wlan0&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
